  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC265">
          <l>maṉṟaveṉ kiḷavi tēṟṟañ ceyyum</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/164/mode/1up">164</ref>.</p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC265-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘kārmaṉṟa eṉpavaḷ kaṇṇuḷḷē kātalar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC265-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>tērmaṉṟat tōṉṟiya’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟakkāl, teḷintaḷ avaḷ eṉṟavāṟu.   (17)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n214/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n215/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. maṉṟaveṉṉuñcol, teḷivup poruṇmaiyai yuṇarttum e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u – m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC265-Cena-cit1">
       <l>‘kaṭavu ḷāyiṉu māka ―</l>
       <l>maṭavai maṉṟa vāḻiya murukē’<app><note>naṟ. 34</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum. maṭavaiyēyeṉṟavāṟām.	(17)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/294/mode/1up">294</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/295/mode/1up">295</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu
      </p>
      <p>
(i–ḷ) maṉṟa eṉ kiḷavi tēṟṟañ ceyyum ― am maṉṟaveṉṉuñ coṟ ṟeḷivup poruṇmaiyai yuṇarttu meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC265-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>maṭavai maṉṟa vāḻiya murukē!</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa maṉṟa vaṟiyāmaiyaiyē teḷivittatu.  <term xml:lang="en">(17)</term>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n181/mode/1up">174</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n182/mode/1up">175</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ.: ― maṉṟa eṉṉuñ col tēṟṟap poruṇmaiyai uṇarttum. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u–m ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC265-Tey-cit1">
        <l>kaṭavu ḷāyiṉu māka ―</l>
        <l>maṭavai maṉṟa vāḻiya murukē<note place="foot">naṟṟiṉai. 34.</note></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟa vaḻik, kaṭavuḷāyiṉum maṭavai eṉat tēṟṟap poruṇmai kāṭṭiṟṟu.	[17]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
